      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "四刀斧手"
      ],
      "text": "闪开了！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00002",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛丁山"
      ],
      "text": "这其间才息我凌云壮志，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00003",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四刀斧手、薛丁山同上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00004",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛丁山"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，圣上啊！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00005",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "薛丁山"
      ],
      "text": "枉争战数十年扶保华夷。太宗皇承高祖开基创业，扫北番平辽蛮御驾征西。仁慈君待薛家君臣大义，沐天恩三辈王世代锦衣。生逆子小薛刚英雄无比，仗王爵每日里惹祸招非。一家人俱遭下叛逆法律，叹功劳到头来烟灭灰飞。忠良臣为国家岂把命惜，",
      "text_length": 110
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00006",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛丁山"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，圣上啊！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00007",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "薛丁山"
      ],
      "text": "大限到谁顾得儿女夫妻。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00008",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛丁山坐下场椅。二刽子手、樊梨花同上。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00009",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "樊梨花"
      ],
      "text": "薛门中生薛刚祸根又起，此乃是天注定谁敢改移。掌权臣尽都是一群叛逆，",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00010",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊梨花"
      ],
      "text": "啊王爷，哎呀夫呀！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00011",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "樊梨花"
      ],
      "text": "夫与妻顷刻间一命归西。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00012",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛丁山"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，夫人呀！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00013",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "薛丁山"
      ],
      "text": "这是你养娇儿长他志气，祸临头才知道后悔也迟。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00014",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛丁山"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，夫人，这是你生的好子，连累一门，刀刀见血，尽作无头之鬼呀。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00015",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊梨花"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，王爷，这是前世之孽，今生来报。可记得在西凉滴泪斩杨凡？转世杀尽薛氏一门，这是冤冤相报了。",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00016",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "樊梨花"
      ],
      "text": "前世里结冤仇今生难避，善与恶福与祸到头无亏。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00017",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛丁山"
      ],
      "text": "夫人呀！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00018",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "薛丁山"
      ],
      "text": "法场上绑得我头晕眼迷，一家人遭诛戮血泪湿衣。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00019",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四军牢、四枪手引武三思同上。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00020",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "武三思"
      ],
      "text": "奉王旨监斩的罪臣叛逆，法场上只哭得日色昏迷。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00021",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "武三思进内案坐，二刽子手同迎接。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00022",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "武三思"
      ],
      "text": "时辰已到，将薛家满门开刀。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00023",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二刽子手"
      ],
      "text": "啊，请王爷升天。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006049_e00024",
      "play_id": "02006049",
      "scene_id": "02006049_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
